My bride Veda, an absolute no makeup person . Very sceptical she was to get her makeup done as her major scare in makeup was over done cakey makeup❤️🌺 .
So glad I could deliver what she wanted and I could deliver natural true to her skin makeup❤️🌺. 
.
It was certainly a big risk she took with that red lip and look how stunning she looked ❤️🌺
.
